<inglise> Article 12 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 12 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall establish procedures whereby experiments themselves or the details of persons conducting such experiments shall be notified in advance to the authority. </inglise>
