<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> On the basis of requests for authorization and notifications received, and on the basis of the reports made, the authority in each Member State shall collect, and as far as possible periodically make publicly available, the statistical information on the use of animals in experiments in respect of: </inglise>
