<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Breeding and supplying establishments shall record the number and the species of animals sold or supplied, the dates on which they are sold or supplied, the name and address of the recipient and the number and species of animals dying while in the breeding or supplying establishment in question. </inglise>
