<inglise> Article 18 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 18 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Each dog, cat or non-human primate in any breeding, supplying or user establishment shall, before it is weaned, be provided with an individual identification mark in the least painful manner possible except in the cases referred to in paragraph 3. </inglise>
