<inglise> (b) sufficient trained staff shall be provided; </inglise>
<eesti> b) tagatakse piisav v&auml;lja&otilde;petatud personal; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) adequate arrangements shall be made for the provision of veterinary advice and treatment; </inglise>
<eesti> c) korraldatakse piisav veterinaarn&otilde;ustamine ja -ravi; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) a veterinarian or other competent person should be charged with advisory duties in relation to the well-being of the animals. </inglise>
<eesti> d) tehakse veterinaararstile v&otilde;i muule p&auml;devale isikule &uuml;lesandeks olla n&otilde;ustajaks loomade heaolu k&uuml;simustes. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Experiments may, where authorized by the authority, be conducted outside user establishments. </inglise>
